OL,3,CHundreds take on sea dip in memory of
OL,4,Ccolleague
OL,6,FHundreds of former marines and service
OL,7,Fveterans honoured a colleague by
OL,8,Ftaking part in a cold water dip in
OL,9,FExmouth.
OL,11,FEx-40 commander marine Tim Crossin
OL,12,Faimed to brave over 30 cold water dips
OL,13,Faround the British coastline in his
OL,14,F"Cold Dip Commando" challenge, but
OL,15,Fsadly passed away from cancer in
OL,16,FDecember 2024 before he could complete
OL,17,Fit.
