OL,3,CHundreds take on sea dip in memory of
OL,4,Ccolleague
OL,6,FTim had raised more than #27,000 for
OL,7,Fthe Royal Marine Charity, Lymphoma
OL,8,FAction, Rock 2 Recovery and the Bowra
OL,9,FFoundation.
OL,11,FOn Thursday 2 January - a day where
OL,12,Ftemperatures were below freezing -
OL,13,Fcolleagues took it upon themselves to
OL,14,Ffinish Tim's challenge in the "Cold
OL,15,FDip Tour" and raised another #10,000
OL,16,Fin his memory.
OL,18,FJohn Justice joined the marines with
OL,19,FTim in 1980.
