OL,3,CHundreds take on sea dip in memory of
OL,4,Ccolleague
OL,6,FHe said: "The thing is with Tim, he
OL,7,Fsort of epitomised the commando spirit
OL,8,F- with the way he carried on through
OL,9,Fhis illness.
OL,11,F"He never said die and went all the
OL,12,Fway to the end, fighting his way,
OL,13,Fraising as much money as he possibly
OL,14,Fcould."
OL,16,FVic Drinkwater had joined Tim in his
OL,17,Flast cold water dip last month.
