OL,3,CHundreds take on sea dip in memory of
OL,4,Ccolleague
OL,6,FShe said: "It was amazing. There were
OL,7,Fpeople that hadn't seen each other for
OL,8,F30 years that met up on a random beach
OL,9,Fto go in the sea and dip just because
OL,10,FTim inspired them to do that.
OL,12,F"And he's done it even now when he's
OL,13,Fnot with us, we are still inspired to
OL,14,Fgo in there and do it for him."
OL,16,FSimon Wright, of the Royal Marines
OL,17,Fcharity, said: "He was just part of
OL,18,Fthe family, part of the Royal Marines
OL,19,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
