OL,3,CHundreds take on sea dip in memory of
OL,4,Ccolleague
OL,6,F"We've all done the same things and we
OL,7,Fwill all do the same thing for each
OL,8,Fother as time goes on so it's
OL,9,Fimportant just to come down and do it,
OL,10,Fremember him but keep that legacy
OL,11,Fgoing - it could be you tomorrow."
OL,13,FThe Cold Dip Tour visits Plymouth on
OL,14,FFriday 3 January, then Land's End and
OL,15,FWestward Ho! the following weekend -
OL,16,Fbefore going right round Britain via
OL,17,FJohn o'Groats and finishing at the end
OL,18,Fof January near Tim's home in Dorset.
